	dprr:hasNoteText "Lucilius 467-468 M. Under this name Lucilius satirized some Quaestor whose real name is lost. See Cichorius, Untersuch. Lucil. 317-320, possibly Tuticanus Gallus (cf. Caes. BC 3.71)." ;
